<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-02-08T08:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-02-08T08:00:00-05:00" n="63" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d63">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 861.00/1066</note>
                            <head><hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Japan</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_MRS1" type="from"><hi rend="italic">Morris</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss></hi></head>
                            <opener>
                                <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                            </opener>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Tokyo</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-02-08T22:00:00+09:00"><hi rend="italic">February
                                            8, 1918, 10 p.m.</hi></date>
                                    <lb/> [<hi rend="italic">Received February 8, 10.40
                                    a.m.</hi>]</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>French Ambassador has just received instructions from his Government
                                to join his British colleague in acceding to request of the Japanese
                                Government reported my telegram of January 17, 5 p.m.,<note n="1" xml:id="d63fn1"><hi rend="italic">Ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_29">p. 29</ref>.</note> for free hand in the
                                event of intervention in Siberia. British Ambassador has as yet
                                received no reply from his Government.</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed><persName corresp="#p_MRS1"><hi rend="smallcaps">Morris</hi></persName></signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>